#: ../../../admin-guide/mm/damon/start.rst:25
msgid "User Space Tool"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../admin-guide/mm/damon/start.rst:27
msgid ""
"For the demonstration, we will use the default user space tool for DAMON, "
"called DAMON Operator (DAMO).  It is available at https://github.com/"
"damonitor/damo.  The examples below assume that ``damo`` is on your "
"``$PATH``.  It's not mandatory, though."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../admin-guide/mm/damon/start.rst:32
msgid ""
"Because DAMO is using the sysfs interface (refer to :doc:`usage` for the "
"detail) of DAMON, you should ensure :doc:`sysfs </filesystems/sysfs>` is "
"mounted."
msgstr ""

