msgstr ""

#: ../../../admin-guide/mm/damon/start.rst:98
msgid ""
"The line of the commands run the artificial memory access generator program "
"again.  The generator will repeatedly access two 100 MiB sized memory "
"regions one by one.  You can substitute this with your real workload.  The "
"last line asks ``damo`` to record the access pattern in the ``damon.data`` "
"file."
msgstr ""

